        <abstract>
            <p>Sorry to hear about condition of JDH’s grandfather.</p> 
<p>Sends proofs of Galapagos chapter of <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Grieves to hear labels are displaced on his plants.</p> 
<p>May he annotate [F. Gérard’s] <hi rend="italic">L’espèce</hi> [(1844), extracted from <hi rend="italic">Dictionnaire universel d’histoire naturelle</hi>, ed. C. D. d’Orbigny (1839–49)]?</p> 
